data.description: Amazing custom home built in 2012! This 5 bedroom, 3 bath home has a gorgeous, large kitchen with Corian counter tops, beautiful tile backsplash, Huge island, and Beautiful custom-built knotty alder cabinets.  The 3 full bathrooms also include custom knotty alder cabinets and tile backsplashes.  Other great features in this home include High-end Moen plumbing fixtures on all faucets, Tons of storage (including 2 large cold storage areas and a large closet in the family room), Beautiful laminate flooring throughout walkways and kitchen, custom molding/chair rail woodwork upstairs, and a comfortable finished basement.  The master bathroom has a garden tub surrounded by beautiful tile and a double shower.  This home also includes a cute front porch, a huge back porch, and a fully vinyl fenced landscaped yard with automatic sprinkler system.  In addition to all of these amazing features, this home boasts a completely finished 3 car attached garage with a sink, a detached 1 car garage/shop and RV parking!!!  This is a great family home on a cul-de-sac in an amazing neighborhood, less than a 1/4 mile from the hospital, and close to shopping.  Please call or text for a showing at 208-421-5157.  REALTOR'S WELCOME!
data.whatILove: We are moving because of a great job opportunity in a different state, which forces us to sell our amazing home!!  One of the things we are really going to miss about this home is the incredible kitchen.  We LOVE all the cabinet space, and the built-in china cabinet is beautiful!  We added an entire wall of cabinets and the china cabinet in 2013.  The other amazing feature of this home is how much storage space it has.  Having a huge food storage area and 2 other large storage areas has been a great luxury.  The massive three car attached garage and the detached one car garage/shop makes this house an absolute winner and a home we will truly miss!   We have improved this already amazing home in the past year by adding a vinyl fence, vinyl porch railings, rock veneer, custom cabinets above the toilets in all three bathrooms, an entire wall of custom cabinets in the kitchen, laminate flooring in the kitchen and all upstairs walkways, and faux wood blinds on all windows.  There is a wonderful family environment with great neighbors, walking and biking paths, and a neighborhood playground and picnic areas.
